verbose_text: We also tested anti-TfR1 3B8 2A1, anti-TfR1 H68.4, anti-MDA 1F83, and anti-4-HNE ab46545 antibodies in camptothecin induced apoptosis; a cleaved PARP antibody was used to detect the induction of apoptosis (XREF_FIG).
